My 2nd mg_course map for the Furaxx team (http://www.forumfuraxx.com/forum). Map created by Me and my Friend Artek and a friend of my friend Xmortel.
Your laboratory has been victim of a disaster. You must escape the area and survive the traps all along your way
It has 12 traps and 2 bonus. Two good music are hidden in the map with... one big secret...

Enjoy !
